Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.450 --> 00:00:13.500
 To create a new training you have to go to Training and select New training 

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:15.800
 then choose Virtual Reality 

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:19.400
 Select the terrain from which you want to make the training 

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:30.100
 you get a top view of the terrain 

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:35.000
 by scrolling with the mouse you can zoom in and out on the terrain 

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:38.400
 you can determine the starting point by double clicking with the left mouse button 

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:48.900
 and double click on the further route to map out a route 

00:01:04.100 --> 00:01:07.500
 You can change the route by dragging one of the numbers 

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:02.100
 If the trail has been created, give the trail a name and press Save 

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:13.500
 If you want to adjust an existing course, go to Training - Adjust Training 

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:17.300
 select the terrain and then the training program 

00:02:21.700 --> 00:02:25.890
 You can then adjust the course by picking up the Start of Finish and moving or grabbing 

00:02:25.890 --> 00:02:28.800
 one of the numbered points and move it 

00:02:34.150 --> 00:02:37.600
 via "Adjust training" you will lose all the old scores 

